    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is Rewrite HF?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The stories that weren't told in Rewrite's main storyline are right here!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our hero, Tennouji Kotarou, has been pulled into a destiny that revolves around the stars. But that wasn't the only destiny that he rewrote. What awaits after he made his choice is the existence of countless potential realities. And amongst those, there is even a future that's as lively as a festival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kazamatsuri, the eco city, is the stage for numerous stories where the spotlight shines on each heroine. Some of the heroines' stories take place after the original story, and others are completely different potential stories. From romance to slapstick comedy, there's a plethora of new stories for Kotori, Chihaya, Akane, Sizuru, Lucia, and Kagari.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The name 'Harvest Festival' suits this collection of celebratory spin-off stories that cover a wide variety of genres, and they were all crafted by the entire staff of the original game. Honeymoon-esque days with the heroines, the loss of enjoyable normal life, mysteries that went unsolvedーthese are all things you can greatly enjoy in the world of Rewrite.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ーLet's share the joy of this harvest together.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 unlockable routes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > First person dungeon crawler, &quot;Rewrite Quest&quot;, unlocked after finishing all routes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiple choices to reach various endings </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unlockable CG viewer </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unlockable Music playback </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Instantly swap between English and Japanese display languages</p></li></ul>",
